{"tid":2382212,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"轉數快錄得688萬個登記　約有2萬億港元交易","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T07:59:10.000Z","uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4638b4d49f4290f01b7892e2a769e6313525d2","tid":2382212,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:41:19.000Z","msg":"近年本港流行電子支付，財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇今午(27日)在立法會上回應議員質詢時，截至去年12月，轉數快已錄得688萬個登記，共處理1.7億宗實時交易，涉及約2萬億港元和360億人民幣，並指有逾176萬宗以轉數快繳費的記錄，涉款逾21億港元。<br />\n<br />\n議員何君堯指新式電子支付是電話方式，但以信用卡方式的電子支付屬舊式，認為政府未有大力推動，質疑政府有否作監察。"},{"pid":"ea2029473e6505d59585cb9dd649514ad248df3b","tid":2382212,"uid":332565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"登記左先可以張一萬蚊會滙去海外"},{"pid":"7ca157d9c65a02204a593acd77290c09d84458ad","tid":2382212,"uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"議員何君堯指新式電子支付是電話方式，但以信用卡方式的電子支付屬舊式<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關信用卡咩事<br />\n大把人用緊apple pay google pay比錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯撚定佢口中嘅電話方式係支那寶wechat pay QR CODE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03aa719117c55ee0935f92ae53696b1af4b9feb","tid":2382212,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"&quot;碌&quot; 卡真係開始過時<br />\n而家應該要轉非接觸式"},{"pid":"2af24038c95fde1645df2818c2f5bb0108a590df","tid":2382212,"uid":15988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"大部分都係馬會"},{"pid":"1799d63b5f33e77adf76ca90610b1ce5172780aa","tid":2382212,"uid":22108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾payme<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a864cd12c2ea76ebd438bd5385d45630fb6679","tid":2382212,"uid":64576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b03aa719117c55ee0935f92ae53696b1af4b9feb","tid":2382212,"uid"